role_description: An Ansible role that installs NordVPN on Mac OS X and Windows
role_description_full_overview: This repository contains an Ansible role that installs NordVPN on Mac OS X and Windows. NordVPN is a virtual private network service provider. It has desktop applications for Windows, macOS, and Linux, mobile apps for Android and iOS, as well as an application for Android TV. Manual setup is available for wireless routers, NAS devices and other platforms.
